"'''Republic HoloNet News Core Edition 14:10:03'''" was an in-universe [[HoloNet News (Insider)|Holonet News]] issue published in [[Star Wars Insider 71|''Star Wars Insider'' 71]].

{{Magazine-stub|article}}

==Contents==
*''Senate Ratifies "Reflex Amendment"''
*''Wookiees Refuse Separatist Entreaties''

==Continuity==
This article was mistakenly printed with the incorrect in-universe date of 14:9:04, which corresponded with the date of the previous article released in [[Star Wars Insider 70]], [[Republic HoloNet News Core Edition 14:9:04|HoloNet News 14:9:04]].

